{"tid":1866290,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［警世］冇人討論醫護罷工？","createTime":"2020-02-06T16:14:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T00:02:30.000Z","uid":200288,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"8fe81395240ca150dac9919e4e0d2912e0dc798e","tid":1866290,"uid":200288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T16:14:46.000Z","msg":"所有醫護手足讀咁多年書，做咁耐野，受咁多苦，都係為左個前途。而家佢地全部allin想救香港人，大家可唔可以開少啲廢po。<br />\n<br />\n一人做少少幫下佢地造勢，幫佢地解釋，幫佢地文宣，係咪真係咁難？<br />\n<br />\n啲廢老搶可樂關你撚事咩，醫護手足輸左就輸成世架啦，大家可唔可以醒下，9000幾個勇武嚟㗎...你就算上次街，蒙住面，俾人拉到要坐，咁都起碼可以搏到唔洗俾人拉。 但醫護手足個個實名罷工㗎，佢地同香港人都輸唔起㗎，一齊輸條命㗎...<br />\n<br />\n應承我，幫下醫護手足，炒熱佢，做文宣，俾口罩老人家、親戚嘅時候幫醫護講兩句好說話，唔難㗎。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>我哋唔可以俾醫護勇武自己煎熬落去</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"5deefaaec407838ec14571eebf6edc3917d195e3","tid":1866290,"uid":202226,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T16:16:19.000Z","msg":"講得啱 醫護罷工咁重要都咁少人理"},{"pid":"be48000da85f47059257747692192157e2eb5ef7","tid":1866290,"uid":200288,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5deefaaec407838ec14571eebf6edc3917d195e3","tid":1866290,"uid":202226,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T16:16:19.000Z","msg":"講得啱 醫護罷工咁重要都咁少人理"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T16:17:55.000Z","msg":"真係痴撚線，醫護今鋪allin每日罷工都係煎熬，一開熱門成堆垃圾po"},{"pid":"f76e8cc3c31bf7a7107db074fb398c2033848f12","tid":1866290,"uid":62512,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T16:18:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聽日醫管員工陣線第一時間一定要默哀，悼念李文亮醫生， connect全中國人！！</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fe4854cb0c76f2d9f6694458926915604bf2f7b","tid":1866290,"uid":200288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T16:18:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f947dcb1e33171150becabaa4cff30e9870aa1ab","tid":1866290,"uid":156913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f76e8cc3c31bf7a7107db074fb398c2033848f12","tid":1866290,"uid":62512,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T16:18:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聽日醫管員工陣線第一時間一定要默哀，悼念李文亮醫生， connect全中國人！！</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T16:19:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c893122f4f54b564d77deb8f11cc57d808a7881","tid":1866290,"uid":182471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T16:25:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0fc6e35995ecd4b8899c2e0c296f9eff4217341d","tid":1866290,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T16:29:07.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"998de694ccd072abbd699f411a6f3c1e27c3ba72","tid":1866290,"uid":73143,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T16:29:12.000Z","msg":"[香港人，反抗] 要贏，必須升級至 全民三罷，甚至 全民勇武<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1866282\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1866282</a><br />\n<br />\n無論係 <span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">勇武</span></strong></span> 或者 <strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">罷緊工</span></span></strong> 既手足 都捱唔到好耐<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">「我地以為一二一二係衝，點知人地一二一二係退既。」<br />\n<br />\n「望返後面已經冇晒人。」<br />\n<br />\n「如果佢話三罷，或者罷鐵、罷藍舖頭，講完你要真係做先得架。」</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n擺在面前有兩套方法，<br />\n其一是  <span style=\"color: limegreen;\">全民有心理準備作正面衝突</span>，<br />\n其二是  <span style=\"color: limegreen;\">全民落實罷工</span><br />\n<br />\n「但係好多人就係覺得，去到呢個樽頸唔知點做。其實佢心入面明明就知呢兩樣野。」</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>「希望大家唔好淨係識得講香港人反抗，反抗係做出嚟架，唔係你鳩噏架！」</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">「我地個個都有夢想架，我地個個都有啲野想做，但係，我地肯犧牲嗰啲野嚟上前線爭取啊！」</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n勇武 同 醫護 都唔係condom，<br />\n所有珍惜生命既香港人，<br />\n以及願意付出更多既抗爭者，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">請你地加入呢次罷工！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n對於全民勇武已經唔抱太大既希望，但係呢次武漢肺炎係一個發動罷工既大好機會<br />\n希望全香港人可以真正團結一次<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9vzoa9L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9vzoa9L.png&h=f8666165&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4cfc2907f75c9db60441c5f66bff308aa1bd7469","tid":1866290,"uid":37722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T16:30:32.000Z","msg":"出面好多垃圾po<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同醫護手足一樣， 罷左一星期<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"395fa68a7570e1e29490aed19123d52728a2c63f","tid":1866290,"uid":269061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T16:30:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eccddb74ae792833636e339167b9478775cafd3b","tid":1866290,"uid":62369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T16:31:29.000Z","msg":"Twitter 好多手足都有去外媒同外國議員到講解醫護罷工<br />\n一齊加入我哋啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTwitter組24小時keep住更新<br />\n幫手retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><i